    <item>
      <title>韩国或考虑增加美国食品进口以安抚特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/south-korea-may-consider-more-us-food-imports-to-placate-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，如果唐纳德·特朗普新政府上台后，两国之间的贸易不平衡问题成为紧张点，韩国可能会考虑增加从美国的食品进口量，以帮助减少这一问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/south-korea-may-consider-more-us-food-imports-to-placate-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 10:30:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫称拜登将减刑另外 2,500 人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/biden-will-commute-another-2-500-sentences-white-house-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫周五在一份声明中表示，总统乔·拜登将减轻近 2,500 名非暴力毒品犯罪分子的刑期，这些犯罪分子的刑期比现行标准规定的刑期要长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/biden-will-commute-another-2-500-sentences-white-house-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
